<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, innitial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="assets/images/icon.png" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="assets/css/wc3.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/student_interface.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
    <script src="js/socket.io.js" defer></script>
    <script type="module" src="js/student.js" defer></script>

    <title><%= user.accountType %> | <%= user.name %> | <%= user.level %></title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="accInfo">
      <output class="myData" style="display: none"><%=user._id %></output>
      <output class="myData" style="display: none"><%=user.level %></output>
    </div>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg timetableNav">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
          <img src="assets/images/icon.png" alt="" width="60" height="40" />
        </a>

        <button
          class="navbar-toggler"
          type="button"
          data-bs-toggle="collapse"
          data-bs-target="#navbarNavAltMarkup"
          aria-controls="navbarNavAltMarkup"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-label="Toggle navigation"
        >
          <i class="fa fa-bars" style="color: white; font-size: 24px"></i>
        </button>

        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNavAltMarkup">
          <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto p-2 bd-highlight">
            <a class="nav-link" aria-current="page" id="timetable" href="#">Timetable</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="w3-row">
      <div class="w3-quarter w3-container w3-hide-small">
        <div class="w3-card-4 w3-round-large w3-animate-top">
          <div class="w3-container notice">
            <p class="mt-4">
              <span>Welcome <%= user.name %></span><br />
              You can view the most recent timetable by clicking on the get timetable button
            </p>
            <hr />
            <p class="mb-5">Specialty: <%= user.specialty %> <br />Level: <%= user.level %></p>
            <hr />
            <p class="mt-4" id="periodInfo"></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w3-half w3-container timetable">
        <div><h1>WEEKLY SCHEDULE</h1></div>
        <div class="w3-small w3-text-grey">UPLOADED :</div>

        <div class="w3-card w3-display-container">
          <div class="table-responsive" id="displayTTContainer"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- <nav id="pagination" aria-label="Page navigation example"></nav> -->
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w3-container">
      <hr />
      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Harum, id voluptatibus! Aliquid,
        aliquam. Vero a magnam tempora pariatur repudiandae eius labore nam nemo soluta esse
        reprehenderit perspiciatis molestias, eveniet cumque. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet
        consectetur, adipisicing elit. Nobis, veniam nisi voluptatum earum illo consequatur quisquam
        ullam laborum ipsum in velit saepe nostrum provident et doloribus culpa beatae consectetur
        eveniet! Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Facilis omnis, assumenda
        mollitia nobis quis nihil quos. Consectetur sint laudantium aperiam qui doloremque quod
        explicabo consequuntur tempora, at facere veritatis velit!
      </p>
    </div>

    <script src="assets/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
